-3-visibility-TTK.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Call-Of-Duty-Modern-Warfare-3-visibility-TTK-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Call-Of-Duty-Modern-Warfare-3-visibility-TTK-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Call-Of-Duty-Modern-Warfare-3-visibility-TTK-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Call-Of-Duty-Modern-Warfare-3-visibility-TTK-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Call-Of-Duty-Modern-Warfare-3-visibility-TTK-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3513953" class="wp-caption-text"> 《使命召唤：现代战争 3》图片来源：动视暴雪。</figcaption></figure><p>斯宾塞在<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cgxuEV8xqEM" target="_blank" rel="noopener">最新一集的 Xbox 官方播客</a>中谈到了这些问题，并重申 Xbox 的独家内容并不在微软对该系列的愿景中（来自<a href="https://www.videogameschronicle.com/news/xbox-boss-pledges-no-more-exclusive-call-of-duty-skins-or-timed-content/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Video Games Chronicle</em></a> ）。</p><p> “对于 PlayStation 上的<em>《使命召唤》</em>玩家以及未来的任天堂玩家来说，我希望你们能够百分百地感受到自己是社区的一部分，”首席执行官说道。</p><p> “我不希望你觉得你错过了一些内容，你错过了一些皮肤，你错过了一些时机......这不是目标。”</p><p>从历史上看，该系列优先考虑 PlayStation 上的内容—— <em>《使命召唤：现代战争 2》</em>为玩家提供每月独家双倍经验点活动、与其他 PlayStation 玩家组队时的武器奖励以及额外的装载槽等功能。 </p><figure id="attachment_3513874" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3513874" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3513874" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Call-Of-Duty-Modern-Warfare-3-2009-maps.jpg" alt="《使命召唤：现代战争 3》。图片来源：动视暴雪。" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Call-Of-Duty-Modern-Warfare-3-2009-maps.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Call-Of-Duty-Modern-Warfare-3-2009-maps-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Call-Of-Duty-Modern-Warfare-3-2009-maps-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Call-Of-Duty-Modern-Warfare-3-2009-maps-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Call-Of-Duty-Modern-Warfare-3-2009-maps-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Call-Of-Duty-Modern-Warfare-3-2009-maps-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3513874" class="wp-caption-text"> 《使命召唤：现代战争 3》图片来源：动视暴雪。</figcaption></figure><p>这不会在<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/xbox-one">Xbox One</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/xbox-series-xs">Xbox Series X|S</a>的未来条目中重复。斯宾塞承诺：“我们的目标是尽可能在所有平台上实现 100% 的发布和内容平等。”</p><p> “我说‘尽我们所能’是因为显然有些平台存在分辨率和帧速率差异，只是基于性能，但除此之外别无其他。</p><p> “我们的目标不是试图通过<em>《使命召唤》</em>来让你购买 Xbox 主机。我希望<em>《使命召唤》</em>国家能够感受到所有平台的支持。</p><p> “我们一直在某些皮肤 [交易] 的另一边，甚至这个 [<em>使命召唤：现代战争 3</em> ] 测试版也没有在第一周出现在 Xbox 上......我认为这对社区没有帮助，我不认为这对游戏有帮助。 </p><figure id="attachment_3511884" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3511884" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3511884" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/call-of-duty-modern-warfare-3-cheating-in-beta.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/call-of-duty-modern-warfare-3-cheating-in-beta.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/call-of-duty-modern-warfare-3-cheating-in-beta-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/call-of-duty-modern-warfare-3-cheating-in-beta-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/call-of-duty-modern-warfare-3-cheating-in-beta-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/call-of-duty-modern-warfare-3-cheating-in-beta-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/call-of-duty-modern-warfare-3-cheating-in-beta-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption