/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/paris_hilton_2023-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/paris-hilton">帕丽斯·希尔顿 (Paris Hilton)</a>将于明年发行新专辑，由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sia">Sia</a>担任执行制作。</p><p>这位歌手兼电视名人证实，她目前正在制作新唱片，并将于本周晚些时候推出她与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/steve-aoki">史蒂夫青木</a>共同制作的新歌《Lighter》。这张专辑将成为她 2006 年发行的首张专辑《Paris》的后续作品。</p><p>本周早些时候，希尔顿在<em>吉米·法伦主演的《今夜秀》节目</em>中说道：“是的，我现在正在录制新专辑。”</p><p>谈到与青木的合作，她补充道，“他太棒了。我们已经是 20 年的朋友了。我很爱他。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="帕丽斯·希尔顿 (Paris Hilton) 畅谈她与史蒂夫·青木 (Steve Aoki) 合作的歌曲以及她由 Sia 制作的专辑 |今夜秀" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/qMwGRCGF3Hk?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>希尔顿专辑的标题和发行日期的详细信息尚未公布，不过《Lighter》将出现在 Aoki 即将于 11 月 17 日发行的第十张录音室专辑《HiROQUEST: Double Helix》中。<a href="https://hiroquest.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此</a>预订。</p><p>本月早些时候，还有消息称<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/a24-adapt-paris-hiltons-memoir-television-series-3510557">希尔顿的回忆录将被改编成电视剧</a>。</p><p>这本<em>《纽约时报》</em>畅销书名为<em>《巴黎：回忆录》</em>于今年早些时候发行，并将由制作公司 A24 开发一个系列，该公司以<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/everything-everywhere-all-at-once"><em>《万物皆可》</em></a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/midsommar-film-review-genuinely-horrifying-2524539-2524539"><em>《仲夏夜惊魂》</em></a>等电影而闻名。该剧集将由《Elle》范宁和达科塔·范宁制作，希尔顿本人担任执行制片人。</p><p>希尔顿在 2000 年代初期作为社交名流和模特而声名鹊起，并于 2003 年至 2007 年通过真人秀<em>《简单生活》</em>吸引了全球观众。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="帕丽斯·希尔顿 (Paris Hilton)、金·佩特拉斯 (Kim Petras) - Stars Are Blind（巴黎版）[官方音乐视频]" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/gCeXqw2pMcs?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>她的首张专辑“Paris”收录了热门单曲“Stars Are Blind”， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/paris-hilton-shares-new-version-of-00s-hit-stars-are-blind-3373048">她在今年年初发行了新录制的版本</a>，名为“Stars Are Blind（巴黎版）”。此外， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-paris-hilton-team-up-with-kim-petras-to-revamp-stars-are-blind-3451089">这首歌还在六月进行了重新混音，</a>由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kim-petras">Kim Petras</a>主演。看看上面的内容。</p><p>今年三月，希尔顿在第四台广播电台的<em>“女性时刻”</em>节目中宣传<em>《巴黎：回忆录》</em>时， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/paris-hilton-spotted-at-picket-line-with-striking-bbc-journalists-3415655">有人看到希尔顿在抗议当地广播电台的罢工期间与纠察线上的 BBC 记者打招呼</a>。</p><p>至于 Sia，这位流行歌星最近宣布了她下一张个人专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sia-shares-gimme-love-and-announces-first-album-in-eight-years-reasonable-woman-3497558">《Reasonable Woman》</a>的详细信息，该专辑将于 2024 年春季通过大西洋唱片公司发行，这也是她八年来的首张个人专辑。她还分享了新单曲“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sia-shares-gimme-love-and-announces-first-album-in-eight-years-reasonable-woman-3497558">Gimme Love</a> ”。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/paris-hilton-to-release-new-album-executive-produced-by-sia-3517198">帕丽斯·希尔顿 (Paris Hilton) 发行新专辑后，由 Sia 担任执行制作的消息</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
詹姆斯·阿瑟 (James Arthur) 表示，他在《X Factor》节目中为了缓解焦虑而吸食了“过量的大麻” https://www.nme.com/news/music/james-arthur-says-he-smoked-an-ungodly-amount-of-weed-to-get-through-anxiety-while-on-x-factor- 3517166?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=詹姆斯-亚瑟-说他在x因素下吸了不敬的大麻量来克服焦虑Hollie GeraghtyWed, 18 Oct 2023 14:00:00 +0000 Music NewsNewsLet's Talk – mental healthPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3517166 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/james-arthur-weed-anxiety-x-factor.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="詹姆斯·阿瑟" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/james-arthur-weed-anxiety-x-factor.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/james-arthur-weed-anxiety-x-factor-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/james-arthur-weed-anxiety-x-factor-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/james-arthur-weed-anxiety-x-factor-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/james-arthur-weed-anxiety-x-factor-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/james-arthur-weed-anxiety-x-factor-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “这一切都有点过分了，这是从床上看电视到全国电视的对比”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/james-arthur-says-he-smoked-an-ungodly-amount-of-weed-to-get-through-anxiety-while-on-x-factor-3517166">詹姆斯·阿瑟 (James Arthur) 表示，他在《X Factor》节目中为了缓解焦虑而吸食了“过量的大麻”，该帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/james-arthur-weed-anxiety-x-factor.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="詹姆斯·阿瑟" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/james-arthur-weed-anxiety-x-factor.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/james-arthur-weed-anxiety-x-factor-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/james-arthur-weed-anxiety-x-factor-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/james-arthur-weed-anxiety-x-factor-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/james-arthur-weed-anxiety-x-factor-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/james-arthur-weed-anxiety-x-factor-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/james-arthur">詹姆斯·阿瑟 (James Arthur)</a>表示，他在参加<em>《X Factor》</em>比赛时吸食了“过量的大麻”来缓解焦虑。</p><p>这位米德尔斯堡歌手凭借单曲“Impossible”赢得了 2012 年英国独立电视台真人秀歌唱比赛第九季的冠军。</p><p>亚瑟曾公开谈论过他过去与心理健康问题的斗争，其中包括在<em>《X因素》</em>期间经历过的恐慌症发作。</p><p>这位艺术家现在透露，他十年来经常吸食大麻，包括在整个演出期间，以帮助控制自己的症状。</p><p> “我吸的大麻量超乎想象，大约十年来我每天都吸大麻，”他在接受<em><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=R7iyEMe-MyA" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Private Parts</a></em>播客采访时说道（来自<em><a href="https://www.dailystar.co.uk/showbiz/james-arthur-smoked-ungodly-amount-31213054" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Daily Star</a></em> ）。 “大量的大麻，大量的大麻，偏执使情况变得更糟，是的，喝酒之类的东西。”</p><p>这位《Just Us》歌手还公开了他“第一次严重恐慌发作”的经历，救护车被叫来，亚瑟认为他“快死了之类的”。</p><p>他补充道：“这一切都有点过分了，这是从床上看台到国家电视台的对比，当我参加那个节目时，它正处于其力量的顶峰，就像每周有 1200 万人在观看。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="James Arthur Chat 的 The X Factor，被他的厂牌和新音乐抛弃 |私处播客" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/R7iyEMe-MyA?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>这位歌手表示，当他被西蒙·考威尔的唱片公司 Syco 开除后，他的心理健康状况跌至新低。 “我根本不想来这里。因为我一生努力的事情似乎已经消失了，它回来的可能性为零，百万分之一的机会，”他分享道。</p><p>他补充说，如果他没有找到新的唱片合约，他“可能不会在这里”。这位歌手<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/james-arthur-reveals-loneliness-after-rita-ora-split-made-him-a-sex-addict-2146210">过去曾谈到过与孤独的斗争和性成瘾的痛苦</a>。</p><p> “我开始沉迷于性。我对性上瘾了，就像我对杂草上瘾一样。 I craved sex, I had to have it and I needed it to fill the void and make myself feel better,” he said in his autobiography <em>Back To The Boy</em> .</p><p> Arthur&#39;s fifth album, &#39;Bitter Sweet Love&#39;, is due to be released on January 26, 2024.</p><h2> <strong>For help and advice on mental health:</strong></h2><ul><li> <strong><a href="https://www.helpmusicians.org.uk/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Help Musicians UK – Around the clock mental health support and advice for musicians</a> (CALL MUSIC MINDS MATTER ON: 0808 802 8008)</strong></li><li> <strong><a href="https://www.thecalmzone.net/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">CALM – The Campaign Against Living Miserably</a></strong></li><li> <strong><a href="http://www.musicsupport.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Music Support Org – Help and support for musicians struggling with alcoholism, addiction, or mental health issues</a> (CALL: 0800 030 6789)</strong></li><li> <strong><a href="http://www.youngminds.org.uk/?gclid=CIuC-9ye69ICFQYo0wodX48KPA" target="_blank" rel="noopener">YOUNG MINDS – The voice for young people&#39;s health and wellbeing</a></strong></li><li> <strong><a href="https://www.time-to-change.org.uk/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Time To Change – Let&#39;s end mental health discrimination</a></strong></li><li> <strong><a href="http://www.samaritans.org/how-we-can-help-you/contact-us?gclid=CKyDztKf69ICFSIo0wodYjYL5A" target="_blank" rel="noopener">The Samaritans – Confidential support 24 hours a day</a></strong></li></ul><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/james-arthur-says-he-smoked-an-ungodly-amount-of-weed-to-get-through-anxiety-while-on-x-factor-3517166">James Arthur says he smoked an “ungodly amount of weed” to get through anxiety while on &#39;X Factor&#39;</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
